{"tid":2507431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"來自台灣女科學家徐若冰獲提名任美國防部副部長","createTime":"2021-04-28T04:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T06:48:04.000Z","uid":257227,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"20b2948917bc6a78febd1a8a4bc22749324e01c0","tid":2507431,"uid":257227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:00:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=432756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432756&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0spe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b7dbd174\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432756&h=cc1de7f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=432756</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登提名在台北出生、被稱為「F-35戰機雷達之母」的徐若冰出任國防部副部長。<br />\n<br />\n67歲的徐若冰，10歲時由台灣移民美國，曾任美國空軍科學顧問委員會主席，也是美國國家工程院院士。2011至16年擔任美國陸軍採購、後勤暨科技助理部長。<br />\n<br />\n徐若冰曾主導包括F-35戰機雷達研發等多個美國空軍重要項目，被外界稱為「F-35戰機雷達之母」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登今次提名她擔任國防部研發暨工程部副部長，美國傳媒報道如果提名獲得通過，將是國防部文官系統中擔任最高職位的亞裔美國人。<br />\n<br />\n台仔會唔會又認親認戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b14bbde556564fac17154f8aff7fdf62c94d9d2","tid":2507431,"uid":228868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"支那：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83e83fc9a620c67a2ab366fe010c9c21cb3185b","tid":2507431,"uid":257227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b14bbde556564fac17154f8aff7fdf62c94d9d2","tid":2507431,"uid":228868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"支那：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:02:31.000Z","msg":"咁都